{"tid":1247870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警總餐廳前經理憶6.12警察邊食早餐邊鬧示威學生 為公義翌日即辭職","createTime":"2019-06-21T09:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T13:12:54.000Z","uid":150685,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"958a8e95f449e2878b5abeaebbbac155a3218477","tid":1247870,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:10:15.000Z","msg":"6月12日警方在金鐘暴力清場引發社會反彈，在灣仔警察總部擔任食堂經理的Ricky在翌日辭職。6月16日他接受在HBO播放的《Vice News Tonight》訪問，明言無法再服務警察，「唔可以喺度做落去&hellip;&hellip;我都想我第時嘅仔女，生活喺一個比較安全、比較自由嘅地方，我唔想香港變成大陸。」<br />\n<br />\n「我喺香港出世，我喺香港生活咗38年。」Ricky在香港土生土長，他早前接受外媒《Vice News Tonight》訪問，憶述6月12日在警察總部餐廳當值，見到警察一邊吃早餐、一邊批評示威學生，「佢（警察）都係講學生點樣阻住條路，點樣影響到香港經濟，搞風搞雨呀。」他形容當時警察表現得好有「衝勁」，「佢哋已經上晒full gear（全副武裝），好似一支箭咁等緊射出去。」<br />\n<br />\n當日早上10時Ricky下班，回家後一直失眠。他輕嘆一句，「唔可以喺度做落去。」翌日他決定辭職，6月16日參加反送中遊行，走到警察總部外百感交集，「幾日前我仲喺度（警總）做緊嘢，今日我就企喺度&hellip;&hellip;企喺佢哋嘅對立面嗰度。」<br />\n<br />\nRicky指，參加遊行人數非常多、氣氛更熱烈，自己的訴求有兩點，港府不要控告學生「暴動罪」，承諾撤回修訂《逃犯條例》，「暫緩意思即係話你終有一日會推返出嚟，但我哋要嘅係呢個惡法永遠都唔會出現，如果你哋咁都收唔到（民意），我覺得呢個政府真係好失敗。」<br />\n<br />\n《Vice News Tonight》形容特首林鄭月娥雖然為「政治災難」致歉，但道歉大概並不足夠，林鄭在200萬港人上街遊行反修例後需要做更多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190621/59741777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190621%2F59741777&d=ciqixHjE7SQ%2Bh8bl84MOe5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=496b2f70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190621%2F59741777&h=d1eedf4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190621/59741777</a>"},{"pid":"2770d8cb5e30e96ebf99f77c0f5dcfb39a0873fa","tid":1247870,"uid":54303,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:11:10.000Z","msg":"警犬咁仇視言論自由 可以死去深圳河以北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4e6c8ca410cdb4717c9f813b15a72de205b2c0","tid":1247870,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:11:40.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3a46181d0e468b0882a9ed57218c641fb833d1d8","tid":1247870,"uid":254022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑警死全家</span></span>"},{"pid":"8bc05d8feaee58752fd57ba86b491615d9104525","tid":1247870,"uid":26333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:13:36.000Z","msg":"好勇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾日前我仲喺度（警總）做緊嘢，今日我就企喺度&hellip;&hellip;企喺佢哋嘅對立面嗰度。"},{"pid":"1858953fcff8bb7f317ca673bb26aeeac853a5a9","tid":1247870,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b90e7f3c33e6ddabfd093b747e6231e0f09bdf","tid":1247870,"uid":218865,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:14:26.000Z","msg":"警犬冇一隻無辜<br />\n身邊起碼有兩隻<br />\n冇參加過佔領但都當市民係賤民<br />\n真心係會覺得學生係暴徒<br />\n要大大力照頭扑<br />\n唔駛諗佢地會有良知"},{"pid":"eb5b9a27fd30d237dc2abafa79bb1697057dea22","tid":1247870,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02039c18d164ef21859d7fe3b1f95849ea099dc","tid":1247870,"uid":438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T09:17:05.000Z","msg":"又係擋路同經濟，原來仲同廢老同一個lv<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35a3766ec683999af78e533e7e7f4e361bc22aa","tid":1247870,"uid":83388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s